Dia. 01 Focused Only About Cutting
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 separates the left and the right side, but it is not possible to win the capturing race with this move.
\par
\par White plays hane at 2, then White has three liberties and Black has only two liberties.
\par Black 1 \cf1\b couldn't reduce White's liberties\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par }
