Dia. 02 Thoughtless
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black 1 is a \cf1\b thoughtless move\cf0\b0 .
\par
\par It is good that it takes a liberty from White but it is useless for the capturing race.
\par
\par White cuts with 2 and even if Black plays at 3, White captures at 4 and Black has no solution.
\par
\par Black three \b\'a1\'e3\b0  stones are captured.
\par
\par }
